 h4 Long leapers (knights)[m
 [m
 p.[m
[31m-	A knight captures exactly as a queen in international draughts game: by jumping[m
[31m-	over its enemies, as many times as it can/want but always in the same direction.[m
[31m-	In this respect it is less powerful than a draughts' queen:[m
[31m-	on the following diagram c8 or f6 cannot be captured.[m
[31m-	However, the knight does not have to maximize the number of captured units[m
[31m-	(as is the case in draughts).[m
[32m+[m[32m  A knight captures exactly as a queen in international draughts game: by jumping[m
[32m+[m[32m  over its enemies, as many times as it can/want but always in the same direction.[m
[32m+[m[32m  In this respect it is less powerful than a draughts' queen:[m
[32m+[m[32m  on the following diagram c8 or f6 cannot be captured.[m
[32m+[m[32m  However, the knight does not have to maximize the number of captured units[m
